  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> Idle\n    Idle --> Dialing : dial\n    Dialing --> Ringing : calling\n    Ringing --> Connected : answer\n    Ringing --> Idle : hangup\n    Connected --> Idle : disconnect\n    Connected --> OnHold : hold\n    OnHold --> Connected : resume",
