  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个电话呼叫的状态图。最开始应该是Idle空闲状态，用户拿起电话拨号就进入Dialing状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Dialing",
        "dial"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Idle是初始状态。那Dialing之后呢？是直接进入Connected接通状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Dialing",
        "Connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是，中间还有个Ringing振铃状态。Dialing拨号完成后进入Ringing，对方接听后才到Connected。另外Ringing的时候如果挂断了，要回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dialing",
        "Ringing",
        "Connected",
        "answer",
        "hangup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上了Ringing状态，还有calling、answer、hangup这几个转移条件。Connected之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ringing",
        "Connected",
        "calling",
        "answer",
        "hangup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "通话中有个功能叫保持，就是OnHold状态。从Connected可以hold进入OnHold，也可以resume恢复回来。最后通话结束disconnect回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connected",
        "OnHold",
        "hold",
        "resume",
        "disconnect",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：OnHold只能resume回到Connected，不能直接disconnect挂断对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnHold",
        "Connected",
        "resume",
        "disconnect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，从OnHold也可以挂断的。我漏说了——OnHold之后resume回Connected，然后才能disconnect。或者我们简化一点，OnHold直接disconnect也行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnHold",
        "Connected",
        "resume",
        "disconnect"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我先按你说的做：OnHold必须resume回Connected才能disconnect。这样逻辑更清晰。图已经画好了，起点是[*]，然后Idle、Dialing、Ringing、Connected、OnHold这几个状态，转移条件也都标上了。",
